videos.description: Texas DB D'Shawn Jamison fields the punt and returns it 71 yards to Utah's six-yard line early in the second quarter.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Texas’ Jamison returns punt 71 yards) 2019/12/31 ESHEET

videos.headline: Texas' Jamison returns punt 71 yards

videos.description: Texas QB Sam Ehlinger goes with the play-fake and then finds an open Collin Johnson for a touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Ehlinger finds Johnson for short TD) 2019/12/31 ESHEET

videos.headline: Ehlinger finds Johnson for short TD

videos.description: Texas head coach Tom Herman jumps in the air Sam Ehlinger's incomplete pass was overturned to an interception by Utah DB Javelin Guidry because it puts the Utes in worse field position.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Texas’ Herman celebrates after Ehlinger’s pass overturned to INT) 2019/12/31 ESHEET

videos.headline: Texas' Herman celebrates after Ehlinger's pass overturned to INT

videos.description: Texas QB Sam Ehlinger sends the ball over to a wide-open Keaontay Ingram for the easy touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Ehlinger finds Ingram open for TD) 2019/12/31 ESHEET

videos.headline: Ehlinger finds Ingram open for TD

videos.description: After Texas QB Sam Ehlinger pitches it back to Keaontay Ingram, Utah DE Maxs Tupai hits Ehlinger late, then shoves him and kicks him as well.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Utah’s Tupai gets flagged for shoving, kicking Ehlinger) 2019/12/31 ESHEET

videos.headline: Utah's Tupai gets flagged for shoving, kicking Ehlinger

videos.description: Sam Ehlinger looks like he wants to pitch it but it is covered so he improvises and runs it in for the touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Ehlinger uses his legs to score the TD) 2019/12/31 ESHEET

videos.headline: Ehlinger uses his legs to score the TD

videos.description: Texas QB Sam Ehlinger passes to Devin Duvernay in the end zone, who makes the catch for the touchdown despite being held by Utah DB Javelin Guidry.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Texas’ Duvernay secures TD grab despite interference) 2019/12/31 ESHEET

videos.headline: Texas' Duvernay secures TD grab despite interference

videos.description: Texas RB Keaontay Ingram takes the handoff, breaks multiple tackles and speeds 49 yards for a touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Texas’ Ingram sheds tackles on big TD run) 2019/12/31 ESHEET

videos.headline: Texas' Ingram sheds tackles on big TD run

videos.description: Texas QB Sam Ehlinger throws three touchdowns and runs for another in a 38-10 win over Utah in the Valero Alamo Bowl.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCF Highlight (Ehlinger’s four total TDs leads Texas past Utah) 2019/12/31 ESHEET SOTFULL

videos.headline: Ehlinger's four total TDs leads Texas past Utah
